<h1>Backup & Restore</h1><div class="alert alert-info">Use <code>scripts/backup-production.sh</code> to create encrypted-ready database and file archives. Restore operations require direct server access and are deliberately not exposed through the browser, because handing a web button the power to replace production data is how exciting incident reports are born.</div><div class="card"><table class="table mb-0"><thead><tr><th>Started</th><th>Type</th><th>Status</th><th>File</th><th>Size</th></tr></thead><tbody><?php foreach($rows as $r):?><tr><td><?=e($r['started_at'])?></td><td><?=e($r['backup_type'])?></td><td><?=e($r['status'])?></td><td><?=e($r['filename'])?></td><td><?=number_format((float)$r['size_bytes']/1048576,2)?> MB</td></tr><?php endforeach?></tbody></table></div>
